de.upb.pcm.interpreter.interfaces

Interface IModelAccessFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModelAccessFactory

    public interface IModelAccessFactory
    Model access factory interface for creating pcm and prm model access, as well as pcm model interpreter.
    Author:
    Joachim Meyer

    • Method Detail

      • getPCMModelAccess

        AbstractPCMModelAccess getPCMModelAccess(int modelAccessType,
                                       InterpreterDefaultContext context)
        Gets PCM model access specified by model access type.
        Parameters:
        modelAccessType - the model access Type, e.g. IModelAccessFactory.USAGE_MODEL_ACCESS.
        context - the interpreter default context for the pcm model access, may be null.
        Returns:
        the pcm model access.

      • getPCMModelInterpreter

        AbstractPCMModelInterpreter getPCMModelInterpreter(int interpreterType,
                                                 InterpreterDefaultContext context,
                                                 de.uka.ipd.sdq.pcm.core.composition.AssemblyContext assemblyContext)
        Gets PCM Model interpreter specified by interpreter type.
        Parameters:
        interpreterType - the interpreter Type, e.g. IModelAccessFactory.RDSEFF_INTERPRETER.
        context - the interpreter default context for the pcm model interpreter, may be null.
        assemblyContext - the assembly context. Only necessary for IModelAccessFactory.RDSEFF_INTERPRETER to specify the assembly context of the corresponding component.
        Returns:
        the pcm model interpreter.

        AbstractPMSModelAccess getPMSModelAccess()
        Gets PMS model access.
        Returns:
        the pms model access.
